gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 142, Pistons 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Pistons, 142-113. Pascal Siakam led the way 23 points, seven rebounds, and six assists for the Raptors, with Gary Trent Jr. adding 18 points and three assists in the victory. Stanley Umude tallied 19 points, four rebounds, and three assists for the Pistons in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 6-7 in the regular season, while the Pistons fall to 2-12.
